commit.message:
Support external packages outside the package-user-dir

- Emacs packages from GUIX from example
- autoloads.el will be generated by emacs, so should ignore
- dolist in package-user-dir is not enough packages from final-pkg-list
- Because guix created directory path is not match with name-version, so we
  have to create tmp-dir to rename a directory name

commit.message:
Don't use the shell when running cygpath

This will improve robustness because it will let us cope with very weird paths,
and it will raise an error when cygpath can't be found or exits with a non-zero
status.
